lled with </div><div class="t m3df x35 h28 y397 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">indignation.&quot; The apostles had been guilty of contempt </div><div class="t m3e0 x35 h28 y398 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of court They had deliberately disobeyed the orders of </div><div class="t m3e1 x35 h28 yeb ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the council. The council no doubt thought that they </div><div class="t m21d x35 h28 y399 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">were dealing very mildly with the disciples. They had </div><div class="t m219 x35 h28 y39a ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not done anything to them the first time, but had threat-</div><div class="t m3e2 x35 h28 y39b ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ened them, giving them fair warning for the future. In </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
